{
  "stem": "5103.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it so happened that this people, one of the family members, went outside for some reason or other, to their luck, and they opened the door, and they saw this whole trail of coal, leaving from the warehouse, all the way to this fellow's house, which was not far from where they lived.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Just a few doors up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was nearly murder.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were screaming, yelling, the men up in the loft.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, all these men, they were all there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "God knows how many, nine, 10, 12, I don't know how many there were, all laughing, telling joke.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They said, how can you-- what has happened?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They called the brother-in-law, but at the same time, they started sweeping.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The whole family was out sweeping the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, we were scared stiff.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We said, we can't-- no way can we stay here, no way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're going to get into--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All this time now, we've been so lucky so far.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're not going to do this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my father said there's some name that he knew of, and it was somebody from his mother's side that lived near the Haarlem [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said that he would go and see this person, which is, he had these false papers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was going.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother said, don't go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm scared, I'm scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, he went and he got to these people's place, and they said no.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You can't stay here because there's a problem here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They keep on-- you know, this is too dangerous.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The neighbors are telling about everything, and we've got people watching continually.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we've got somebody else who is my daughter-in-law's someone, son-in-law, and this one is going to have put you up.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they live in-- not far from us.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
